OL,3,CWelsh Labour leadership candidates and
OL,4,Cthe substance behind their promises
OL,6,FThe race is on to be Welsh Labour
OL,7,Fleader and the next First Minister.
OL,9,FVoting has opened and while the
OL,10,Fmajority of us don't have a say, it
OL,11,Fwill have an impact on us all.
OL,13,FVaughan Gething and Jeremy Miles have
OL,14,Fboth held senior cabinet positions,
OL,15,Fboth are former solicitors and both
OL,16,Fbelieve they're the man with a plan
OL,17,Ffor the future. But is there any
OL,18,Fsubstance behind the promises?
OL,19,FPresenter Rob Osborne quizzed them
OL,20,Fboth.
