OL,3,CWelsh Labour leadership candidates and
OL,4,Cthe substance behind their promises
OL,6,FWhat are the candidates' missions for
OL,7,FWales?
OL,9,FVaughan Gething: "My mission is to
OL,10,Fhave a country that's at ease with
OL,11,Fitself - a modern, confident Wales,
OL,12,Fone where we have an economy that
OL,13,Fcreates good jobs and good
OL,14,Fopportunities."
OL,16,FJeremy Miles: "Economic prosperity is
OL,17,Fwhat we need to see in Wales,
OL,18,Fsustainable economic growth, which
OL,19,Fwill create those employment
OL,20,Fopportunities that are high skilled,
OL,21,Fand high paid."
