OL,3,CWelsh Labour leadership candidates and
OL,4,Cthe substance behind their promises
OL,6,FBoth of their manifestos focus heavily
OL,7,Fon the NHS - with lots of spending
OL,8,Fpledges. So where's the money coming
OL,9,Ffrom?
OL,11,FVaughan Gething: "Some of what we want
OL,12,Fto do, does mean we'll need more
OL,13,Fresources because I think for the sort
OL,14,Fof NHS we all want we need resources,
OL,15,Fwe need reform, recruitment and
OL,16,Fretention.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/16
