OL,3,CWelsh Labour leadership candidates and
OL,4,Cthe substance behind their promises
OL,6,F"We don't get a different view on a
OL,7,Ffuture of resources without a change
OL,8,Fof the UK government. After 14 years
OL,9,Fof austerity, all of our choices get
OL,10,Fmore and more difficult.
OL,12,F"When Tony Blair was elected as Prime
OL,13,FMinister in 1997 it took a couple of
OL,14,Fyears before there was significant and
OL,15,Fsustained investment in the economy
OL,16,Fand public services. I think the next
OL,17,FLabour government will have an equally
OL,18,Ftroublesome financial inheritance and
OL,19,Fit will take a medium term before we
OL,20,Fget to the sustained resources."
