OL,4,Cthe substance behind their promises
OL,6,FJeremy Miles: "Our NHS needs more
OL,7,Ffunding, as do all of our public
OL,8,Fservices. But we also need to support
OL,9,Fthe NHS to adapt to face the
OL,10,Fchallenges it faces today and into the
OL,11,Ffuture and there are a number of ways
OL,12,Fwe need to do that.
