OL,3,CWelsh Labour leadership candidates and
OL,4,Cthe substance behind their promises
OL,6,F"Firstly, we have to translate the
OL,7,Fbroad priorities we have for the NHS
OL,8,Finto a set of actionable priorities
OL,9,Ffor the local health boards to make
OL,10,Fsure the targets that we have are
OL,11,Fdelivering the outcomes that we want
OL,12,Fwhich are the critical things and
OL,13,Fgreater accountability within the
OL,14,Fhealth service.
