OL,3,CWelsh Labour leadership candidates and
OL,4,Cthe substance behind their promises
OL,6,F"What we've seen in the last two
OL,7,Frounds of budget reallocations is
OL,8,Ffunding moving towards the NHS because
OL,9,Fof the pressure that it's under and is
OL,10,Fnecessary given those pressures. I
OL,11,Fthink the entire public sector needs
OL,12,Fmore funding, we are giving it as much
OL,13,Ffunding as we can with the budgets
OL,14,Fthat we have. We do need better
OL,15,Fbudgets, that requires a Labour
OL,16,Fgovernment in Westminster."
OL,18,FFavourite Labour Prime Minister - bar
OL,19,FClement Attlee?
OL,21,FJeremy Miles: Harold Wilson
