OL,6,F"The PISA results were disappointing.
OL,7,FWhen I became minister I set out a
OL,8,Fplan to improve literacy and numeracy
OL,9,Fin schools - in education these plans
OL,10,Ftake some years to bare fruit and I'm
OL,11,Fabsolutely confident that by the time
OL,12,Fwe see the next set of PISA results,
OL,13,Fthey'll be on the up as they were in
OL,14,F2018."
