OL,6,F"The apprenticeship budget is directly
OL,7,Faffected by what the Tories have
OL,8,Fdone," he said.
OL,10,F"We now have significantly less money
OL,11,Ffor apprenticeships because the Tories
OL,12,Fchose to keep the power and the money
OL,13,Fin Westminster when we left Europe.
OL,14,FThat has meant a deliberate design
OL,15,Fthat prevents us from putting money
OL,16,Finto apprenticeships."
